TeamHierarchy: Team structure. Columns: Country Manager, Country Manager User ID, RespPersonEmail.

CurMonNBV_ColumnName: NBV display metadata. Columns: Index, NBV_DepName, NBV_Header.

FT2orM2: Unit toggle. Columns: Category, Field.

NBV_Headers: NBV parameter display. Columns: Parameter, Parameter Fields, Parameter Order.

