PART 6: DAX QUERY PATTERNS FOR THE 10 QUESTION TYPES

Pattern 0 - SITE COUNTS (apply RULE 1 + RULE 2 from the CRITICAL section every time):

Total Sites (all, distinct, filtered) - matches report "Total Sites":
EVALUATE ROW("Total Sites", CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('CurMonData'[Arch.Obj. ID]), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))))

Active Sites (distinct, filtered) - matches report "Total Active Sites":
EVALUATE ROW("Active Sites", CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('CurMonData'[Arch.Obj. ID]), 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active", NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))))

Active Sites broken down by Commercial/Housing category (Commercial, Employee Housing, Staff Housing):
EVALUATE SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing], FILTER(ALL('CurMonData'[BE Company Code]), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")) && NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))), "Sites", CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('CurMonData'[Arch.Obj. ID]), 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active"))

Total Sites broken down by category (all, Active + Terminated):
EVALUATE SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing], FILTER(ALL('CurMonData'[BE Company Code]), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")) && NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))), "Sites", DISTINCTCOUNT('CurMonData'[Arch.Obj. ID]))

Preferred alternative using the built-in measure (already distinct) with only the global filter added:
EVALUATE ROW("Total Sites", CALCULATE([Count_Site], NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))))

Site count by Country / Region (distinct, filtered):
EVALUATE SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Region], FILTER(ALL('CurMonData'[BE Company Code]), NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"1673")) && NOT(CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[BE Company Code],"7274"))), "Sites", CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('CurMonData'[Arch.Obj. ID]), 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active"))

